pma_xml_export.pma:structure_schemas:
<pma:database name="" collation="latin1_swedish_ci" charset="latin1">
CREATE TABLE `instagramData` ( `recID` int(255) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `media_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `url` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `c_time` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `user` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `userfullname` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `filter` varchar(2048) NOT NULL, `comment_count` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `caption` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `link` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `low_res` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `thumb` varchar(255) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`recID`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=130 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
CREATE TABLE `persistEntries` ( `id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `min_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
